OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening with clear spells but
OL,7,Fperhaps the odd shower, chiefly in
OL,8,FCumbria. Clouding over through the
OL,9,Fnight and turning windy with gales
OL,10,Fdeveloping in coastal and upland
OL,11,Fregions later. Showery rain developing
OL,12,Flater. Staying mild and frost-free.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FA very windy day with severe
OL,15,Fgales in places. Showery rain through
OL,16,Fthe morning turning heavier and more
OL,17,Fpersistent during the afternoon.
OL,18,FGenerally mild but turning colder in
OL,19,FCumbria later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
