OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FColder
OL,6,Fon Friday with sunny spells and
OL,7,Fshowers, wintry in places. Showers
OL,8,Fpossible on Saturday, but many places
OL,9,Fremaining dry. Further rain on Sunday.
OL,10,FBreezy at times. Frost possible
OL,11,Fovernight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
